OL,3,CEngland prepare to face DR Congo in
OL,4,Cfirst World Cup knockout game
OL,6,FEngland is preparing to face the
OL,7,FDemocratic Republic of Congo in
OL,8,FAtlanta on Wednesday, in their first
OL,9,Fknockout game of the World Cup.
OL,11,FAfter winning 2-0 against Panama to
OL,12,Fsecure the top spot in their group,
OL,13,FEngland head into the knockout stages
OL,14,Flooking to keep themselves on course
OL,15,Fto deliver their first trophy since
OL,16,F1966.
OL,18,FHowever, manager Thomas Tuchel has
OL,19,Fpreviously warned England will be
OL,20,F"punished" if they start to look
OL,21,Fbeyond this knockout match.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@JO]
