OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782902882
OL,3,CEngland prepare to face DR Congo in
OL,4,Cfirst World Cup knockout game
OL,6,FIf England do win, they'll face either
OL,7,FMexico or Ecuador at the Azteca
OL,8,FStadium in Mexico City in the early
OL,9,Fhours of Monday morning.
OL,11,FWhile the starting lineup for
OL,12,FWednesday'd game is yet to be
OL,13,Fannounced, midfielder Declan Rice is
OL,14,Fexpected to return after missing the
OL,15,FPanama match due to a minor hamstring
OL,16,Finjury.
