OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782902882
OL,3,CEngland prepare to face DR Congo in
OL,4,Cfirst World Cup knockout game
OL,6,FITV News took a look at the Atlanta
OL,7,FStadium, which is set to host around
OL,8,F67,000 fans on Wednesday. We saw how
OL,9,Fthe 70,000 capacity venue had been
OL,10,Fchanged to accommodate the larger
OL,11,Fpitch required for a World Cup
OL,12,Ffootball match.
OL,14,FGood Morning Britain Correspondent
OL,15,FAshna Hurynag takes a look inside the
OL,16,FAtlanta Stadium ahead of England's
OL,17,Fmatch against DR Congo
OL,19,FLining up against the Three Lions will
OL,20,Fbe several familiar faces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
