OL,6,FThey opened their campaign with a 1-1
OL,7,Fdraw against Portugal before
OL,8,Frecovering from defeat to Colombia to
OL,9,Fclaim a first World Cup win since 1978
OL,10,Fagainst Uzbekistan, a 3-1 comeback
OL,11,Fvictory, sending them through.
